BEGIN_NAMESPACE_FDO_COMMANDS_NETWORK
public __gc __interface 		INetworkPathReader
 FdoINetworkPathReader is an interface that is used to return the result of a single path from the result returned by the network analysis command. The path is usually made of node features and link features. Some of the analysis commands returns only node features.
